directions: Directions: Going from Fallsville, (Newton County) west on Highway 16 to Red Star (Madison County) turn right on Madison County Road 3605.  Drive right at 1 mile (you will cross over a low water bridge and also a cattle guard) until you come to a "Y" in the road.  There you will see a sign with three cemeteries on it pointing to the right. Follow the road on the right and you will drive about 1.3 miles, and you will see Old Bethel on your left. Go past this cemetery and follow the dirt road. You will see an old, worn down community/church building. You will need to turn on the dirt road to your right there. Park your vehicle there and walk down to the cemetery.  The cemetery is just down the road a bit, not far to walk.
